If(
    ThisItem.Status_Choice.Value = "Booked",
    ColorFade(
        Color.Blue,
        .3
    ),
    ThisItem.Status_Choice.Value = Blank(),
    ColorFade(
        Color.Black,
        .3
    ),
    ColorFade(
        Color.White,
        .3
    )
)

//If(ThisItem.Status_Choice.Value = "Booked",ColorFade(ColorValue("#D2925F"),.3),ColorFade(ColorValue("#3C5F92"),.3))
If(
    ThisItem.Status_Choice.Value = "Booked",
    ColorFade(
        ColorValue("#D2925F"),
        .3
    ),
    Self.Text = "Wrong Day",
    ColorFade(
        Color.Red,
        .0
    ),
    ThisItem.Status_Choice.Value = Blank(),

        Color.LightGreen,
        .0

    ColorFade(
        ColorValue("#3C5F92"),
        .3
    )
